summary: This modification is a change of location \"Mixwater Mill\". This modification is a change of location. File adds new characters, change their home (cleaning from the web and other) and also adds an underground shelter thieves guild.
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://static.skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/37301-1-1371539959.jpg[/img]
List of changes on \"Mixwater Mill\":
1. Added new characters - the sawmill workers.
2. Home cleaned of dirt and cobwebs.
3. There are two horses for the character.
4. Posted underground refuge for the thieves guild. In it, you can live with yourself.
It can be said, the test version, so much still needs work.
author: Kulac
